{"bio":null,"bio_l":"嗜血狂魔史德利古尔是通过仪式严格甄选出的猎手，更准确的说，他是剥皮双子忠实的走狗，他从常年云雾缭绕的噬血之峰被派下去搜寻鲜血。剥皮双子需要海量的鲜血来获得满足和安抚，而如果当地的祭祀没能满足他们，他们就会抽干这个高原王国所有人民的鲜血。因此史德利古尔总是外出进行屠戮。他能榨取出血液之中的生命之力，然后这些能量通过他武器和护甲上的附魔标记立刻流向双子。多年以来，他一直是一条得力的走狗，在战斗时他像豺狼一样残暴。据说，在嗜血狂魔那涌动着对鲜血的渴望的面具之下，能够直视剥皮双子那可怖的嘴脸。","stats":"<img src=\"Int\" alt=\"Intelligence\" />Intelligence:18 + 1.70<br /><img src=\"Agi\" alt=\"Agility\" />Agility:24 + 3.00<br /><img src=\"Str\" alt=\"Strength\" />Strength:23 + 2.00<br /><img src=\"Attack\" alt=\"Damage\" />Damage:29 - 35<br /><img src=\"Speed\" alt=\"Movespeed\" />Movespeed:290<br /><img src=\"Defense\" alt=\"Armor\" />Armor:3.36","stats1":[["Int","Intelligence","18 + 1.70"],["Agi","Agility","24 + 3.00"],["Str","Strength","23 + 2.00"],["Attack","Damage","29 - 35"],["Speed","Movespeed","290"],["Defense","Armor","3.36"]],"detailstats":"<div class=\"redboxContent\"><div class=\"redboxTop\"></div><div id=\"statsInner\"><div id=\"statsLeft\"><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol\">25</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">15</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">1</div>等级</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,879</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,119</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">587</div>生命值</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,024</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">543</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">234</div>魔法值</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">145-151</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">95-101</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">53-59</div>攻击力</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">16</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">9</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">3</div>护甲</div></div><div id=\"statsRight\"><div class=\"statRow\"></div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">1800 / 800</div>视野范围</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">128</div>攻击范围</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">N/A</div>弹道速度</div></div><br clear=\"both\" /></div><div class=\"redboxBottom\"></div></div>","detailstats1":[["生命值","1,879","1,119","587"],["魔法值","1,024","543","234"],["攻击力","145-151","95-101","53-59"],["护甲","16","9","3"]],"detailstats2":[["视野范围","1800 / 800"],["攻击范围","128"],["弹道速度","N/A"]],"abilities":[{"key_name":"bloodseeker_bloodrage","dname":"血之狂暴","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">单位目标</span><br />影响：<span class=\"attribVal\">英雄</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\">魔法</span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\"><font color=\"#70EA72\">是</font></span>","desc":"让一个单位陷入渴望鲜血的狂怒中，使其在持续时间内造成和承受的伤害都会被加深。血之狂暴状态下的英雄杀死一个单位后将回复阵亡单位最大生命值的25%；血之狂暴状态下的英雄被击杀则击杀者将回复阵亡英雄最大生命值的25%。","dmg":"","notes":"血之狂暴可以对敌方单位、友方单位以及血魔自身施放。<br />伤害的制造者和承受者双方距离若超过2200范围则伤害加深效果减半。","attrib":"持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">9 / 10 / 11 / 12</span><br />\n伤害数值提高： <span class=\"attribVal\">25% / 30% / 35% / 40%</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:12/10/8/6","lore":"史德利古尔与人分享他那野兽般的嗜血饥渴。","hurl":"Bloodseeker"},{"key_name":"bloodseeker_blood_bath","dname":"血之祭祀","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">点目标</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\"><font color=\"#d61107\">纯粹</font></span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\">否</span>","desc":"嗜血狂魔用圣血为一片区域洗礼。经过3秒后祭祀完成，区域范围内所有敌人都会受到伤害，并被沉默。","dmg":"","notes":"总时间为0.4秒的施法时间加上2.6秒的生效延迟。","attrib":"祭祀范围： <span class=\"attribVal\">600</span><br />\n沉默持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">3 / 4 / 5 / 6</span><br />\n伤害： <span class=\"attribVal\">120 / 160 / 200 / 240</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:100<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:29/26/23/20","lore":"只要有人在战场上遍洒鲜血，那么剥皮双子就乐于向他施以援手。","hurl":"Bloodseeker"},{"key_name":"bloodseeker_thirst","dname":"嗜血渴望","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">被动</span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\"><font color=\"#70EA72\">是</font></span>","desc":"嗜血狂魔能够感知到整个地图中生命值低于一定百分比的英雄，获得其真实视域并提升嗜血狂魔的移动速度和攻击力。嗜血渴望的效果可以叠加。","dmg":"","notes":"幻象不能触发该技能。","attrib":"触发渴望血量： <span class=\"attribVal\">30%</span><br />\n移动速度提升： <span class=\"attribVal\">10% / 20% / 30% / 40%</span><br />\n伤害： <span class=\"attribVal\">10 / 20 / 30 / 40</span>","cmb":"","lore":"史德利古尔闻到血腥味就会变得无比狂热。","hurl":"Bloodseeker"},{"key_name":"bloodseeker_rupture","dname":"割裂","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">单位目标</span><br />影响：<span class=\"attribVal\">敌方单位</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\"><font color=\"#d61107\">纯粹</font></span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\"><font color=\"#70EA72\">是</font></span>","desc":"让一个敌方单位皮开肉绽。若受到割裂的单位移动，将按移动距离的一定百分比受到伤害。伤害效果无视技能免疫。","dmg":"","notes":"受到割裂作用时不可使用闪烁匕首。","attrib":"持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">12</span><br />\n移动伤害： <span class=\"attribVal\">20% / 40% / 60%</span><br />\n施法距离： <span class=\"attribVal\">1000</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:150/200/250<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:60","lore":"当嗜血狂魔猎杀你时，受伤就意味着死亡。","hurl":"Bloodseeker"}],"itembuilds":{"Starting":["tango","stout_shield","quelling_blade"],"Early":["boots","poor_mans_shield","wraith_band","magic_wand"],"Core":["power_treads","sange_and_yasha","tpscroll"],"Luxury":["radiance","butterfly","mjollnir","invis_sword","black_king_bar","monkey_king_bar","heart","vladmir"]},"skillup":[{"groupName":"常规加点","desc":"<p>回血技能线上两点够了，压力很大可以考虑点3级，禁魔前期升一级对线耗血，配合6级大招杀人，嗜血渴望是血魔核心技能，尽早加满，禁魔11级前加到3级，CD可以使对方一直沉默。</p>","abilityKeys":["bloodseeker_blood_bath","bloodseeker_bloodrage","bloodseeker_blood_bath","bloodseeker_thirst","bloodseeker_thirst","bloodseeker_rupture","bloodseeker_thirst","bloodseeker_thirst","bloodseeker_bloodrage","bloodseeker_bloodrage","bloodseeker_rupture","bloodseeker_blood_bath","bloodseeker_blood_bath","bloodseeker_bloodrage","attribute_bonus","bloodseeker_rupture","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus"]}],"hp":"agility","faction":"dire","name":"Bloodseeker","name_l":"嗜血狂魔","atk":"melee","atk_l":"近战","roles":["Carry","Jungler"],"roles_l":["核心","打野"],"nickname_l":["BS","